{"tid":2140833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃之鋒: 剛好今天已是「八五大三罷」一週年，當刻的堅持還在嗎？","createTime":"2020-08-05T09:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T19:48:37.000Z","uid":41998,"like":146,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"54755e3af96bfef8f4324a1e685f78217b406dd6","tid":2140833,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n不經不覺，剛好今天已是「八五大三罷」一週年，當刻的堅持還在嗎？此時此刻，固然形勢相當艱困，但我們仍想跟大家在一起，好好抵抗。<br />\n...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bt5TWQR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbt5TWQR.png&h=52d2325d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.313299448762570/3211195885639564/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fphotos%2Fa.313299448762570%2F3211195885639564%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeallsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=6f8c909e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.313299448762570/3211195885639564/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">二零一九年，八月五日。</span></strong><br />\n- 新巴有超過200名員工參與罷工，佔車長人數約20%<br />\n- 航空界響應8.5大罷工，估計逾3,000人參與<br />\n- 機管局網站顯示，逾250班航機取消<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n黑警施發1,002枚催淚彈、170枚橡膠子彈及28發海綿彈驅散。<br />\n而且拘捕148人，最年輕一人僅13歲...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NCW4i4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNCW4i4G.jpg&h=72fc1541&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16f1e0cd38b2e5d97b7938dc40b4d0a4fe65a9c3","tid":2140833,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3952f47c6753792383e7234e6a5a89c59eb08e32","tid":2140833,"uid":41998,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"唔係睇到gphone個post，<br />\n我都唔醒起原來已經一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f71970e5d05973e694843988ecf8f69892a320","tid":2140833,"uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"大家都明白的"},{"pid":"7b95fa2bd60e75120b6c6348bf2c7e370a8e210c","tid":2140833,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f71970e5d05973e694843988ecf8f69892a320","tid":2140833,"uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"大家都明白的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1287afd39b34847355faee3a7267a4b2b677dd6c","tid":2140833,"uid":152104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cc4c7c093adbc4cc1a9f6df2f34c230c046350","tid":2140833,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad1dab46e8b1de78d68c1ae8c883022ad9fa90b","tid":2140833,"uid":41998,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iaApjaO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiaApjaO.jpg&h=8cd4bf19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce1f317511237ae30a70c52df325e0792dbb4da7","tid":2140833,"uid":41998